   <p>William Blacks letter has not been found.</p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-02-09-02-0341-fn-0002-ptr" id="GEWN-02-09-02-0341-fn-0002">2</a>

   <p>See <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-02-09-02-0339" class="document">GW to William Black, this date</a>.</p>

</div>
