   <p>See <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-02-09-02-0339&amp;expandNote=GEWN-02-09-02-0339-fn-0007#GEWN-02-09-02-0339-fn-0007" class="document">note 7 in GWs letter to Black of this date</a>.</p>

